# sudoku-game

Sudoku game, made with python & curses. Play in the terminal. For Linux, Mac OS and Windows.


![](doc/screenshot.png)

## How to install

```shell
$ pip install play-sudoku
```

## How to play

```shell
$ sudoku
```

